{
  "stem": "17821.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I don't think she stayed because I felt I was the only one there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But no problem.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was the name of the high school, do you remember?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called the High Pavement Secondary School.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was-- it was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] what's the word for it?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I always had a problem with myself psychologically.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't think I was clever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I was getting top grades at school.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was something wrong with me, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was afraid I wouldn't pass the, the oral.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because you have to pass the oral in a language examination.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I decided I would go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my professor heard about this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he kept me back after class.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he said I didn't have to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Well, I'd made my mind up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I guess that was the way I was, too, when I'd made my mind up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I said I was going.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But, I mean, it has been shown by the ensuing history that I just had to go because that's where I had to meet that young man.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My little sister Violet and I were very fond of one another.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We slept together because in those days, there wasn't a separate bed for each person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There would be two children to a bed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So perhaps my real childhood would be my little sister Violet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "20.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to go back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I hadn't passed my finals.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The exam came later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then we wrote to one another.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I still have a bag full of correspondence of those days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he would write.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I would write.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother for a while hid the letters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then one day, she said, oh, here you are.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You may as well have these.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
